text:
Turn around~
and smile like you've found someone you like!

That's great~
Keep it up today too!

Yes!
Please take care of me today!

You seem to be in good spirits, Chiyuki. The photographer
mentioned that you're making great expressions.

I'm glad...
Did I worry you with what I said last time?

Well, not so much worried... but if there's anything,
I can be someone you can talk to.

After the last shoot,
I had some thoughts...

Trying to act like a bad girl made me appreciate the
times when I'm wearing a dress even more...

Hehe, sorry about that.
I feel like I'm saying strange things...

No, it's fine. Having different sides is what makes you great,
Chiyuki, and I'm glad you're enjoying them yourself.
